104
00:05:42,770 --> 00:05:44,530
So what is a database?

105
00:05:44,530 --> 00:05:48,430
Well, a database is simply some
way to organize your data such

106
00:05:48,430 --> 00:05:54,070
that you can actually create data,
update data, read data, and delete

107
00:05:54,070 --> 00:05:54,580
