deleting data, and even updating it

110
00:06:02,170 --> 00:06:03,550
along the way.

111
00:06:03,550 --> 00:06:06,640
But the database isn't the
only thing in our picture here.

112
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:09,715
We also have a database
